Welcome to the thread of a thousand wonders
Hello welcome to this thread if you read this thread i would like it if you replied
what is the thread of a thousand wonders ?
The thread of a thousand wonders is a thread were you can request a tut , ask help and we can add thing to servers.
What can i do to get a job of the thread of a thousand wonders
Easy you can post a request to become a member there is 3 different jobs
.Tut maker .Error helper .Tut adder to a server
there is no set formate to a request but you have a higher chance to getting a job if you have a neat layout
